### FHIR ServiceRequest — orders routing spine. VERSION_NEUTRAL, /fhir/R4/...

@fhirBase = http://127.0.0.1:3000/fhir/R4

### Create a lab order (replace SUBJECT_ID with a Patient uuid)
POST {{fhirBase}}/ServiceRequest
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

{
  "resourceType": "ServiceRequest",
  "status": "active",
  "intent": "order",
  "category": [
    { "coding": [{ "system": "http://snomed.info/sct", "code": "laboratory", "display": "Laboratory" }] }
  ],
  "code": { "coding": [{ "system": "http://loinc.org", "code": "58410-2", "display": "CBC panel" }] },
  "subject": { "reference": "Patient/SUBJECT_ID" }
}

### Read a ServiceRequest by id
GET {{fhirBase}}/ServiceRequest/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

### Routing poll — active lab orders (the fulfilling-module contract)
GET {{fhirBase}}/ServiceRequest?category=laboratory&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

### Search a patient's orders
GET {{fhirBase}}/ServiceRequest?subject=Patient/SUBJECT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

### Invalid routing code → 422 OperationOutcome
GET {{fhirBase}}/ServiceRequest?category=not-a-category
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}
